=:inbox_tray: *Cited support draft ready for review* <@{{ $('Prepare Research Request').item.json.agentSlackId }}>

*Question:* {{ $('Prepare Research Request').item.json.question }}
*Sources cited:* {{ $('Build Cited Email Reply').item.json.sourceCount }}

The draft is in Gmail. Verify the sources, edit if needed, and send it yourself. This workflow never sends automatically.

=:warning: *Support draft could not be prepared* <@{{ $('Prepare Research Request').item.json.agentSlackId }}>

*Question:* {{ $json.question }}
*Error:* {{ $json.errorMessage }}

